Introduction

Yoon Jongwoo is a South Korean Rapper under ARMADA Ent. He is the Leader of the boy group ONE PACT and a former member of Black Level.

He used to be a member of the boy group 'Black Level' under the stage name Ze:U. In December 2022, he participated in the popular Mnet survival show "Boys Planet," where he finished in 18th place. Despite not making it to the debut lineup of the 9-member boy group, Jongwoo's talent won the hearts of fans worldwide. He was determined to debut in a boy group and worked hard towards his dream.

On September 27, 2023, Armada Entertainment announced Jongwoo as the First Member and Leader of their upcoming boy group ONE PACT.
